# RCA Bot Routine — Environment Variables
#
# No environment variables needed for any of the 3 Routines.
#
# All authentication is handled by the connectors configured in the Routine:
#   - Jira auth    → Atlassian connector (OAuth)
#   - Claude API   → built into the Routine runtime (Enterprise credentials)
#
# Teams posting (Routine 1) is manual: the Routine outputs the formatted message
# to the run log and you paste it into the Teams meeting chat each Monday.
